n, while\nthey remain symmetric in the reduced pair wave approximation, giving the\npossibility to experimentally distinguish between the two approximations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2005 15:56:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2005 19:09:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2005 20:46:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
